headline: FICO Wins Banking Tech Award for Blockchain and AI Innovation
summary: LONDON, December 16, 2024--At the Banking Tech Awards in London, global analytics software leader FICO won the Tech of the Future – Blockchain and Tokenisation award for its innovative work using blockchain technology for AI model governance. FICO’s use of blockchain to advance responsible AI is the first time blockchain has been used to track end-to-end provenance of a machine learning model, to meet responsible AI and regulatory requirements.
